# Netlify redirect rules — proxy API calls to the Python backend.
#
# Once your FastAPI backend is deployed (Railway / Render / Fly.io),
# replace https://api.medblueprints.com with your actual backend URL.
# Then commit + push to trigger a Netlify re-deploy.
#
# Format: FROM   TO   STATUS

/feedback/*    https://api.medblueprints.com/feedback/:splat    200
/query/*       https://api.medblueprints.com/query/:splat       200
/docs          https://api.medblueprints.com/docs               200
/openapi.json  https://api.medblueprints.com/openapi.json       200
